{"tid":848699,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭秀文：肥美的飄紅","createTime":"2018-10-05T06:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T13:33:31.000Z","uid":160977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05e3edae5e127e0aab7d18f30d26e7be87a34755","tid":848699,"uid":160977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"現在的鄭秀文（Sammi）身材弗爆，但大家記不記得初出道時的她，其實是肥妹仔一名，那時的她，笑言真的連喝水都肥。近日Sammi在網上放了九三年拍的劇集《大頭綠衣鬥殭屍》片段，片中的Sammi真是青春，錢小豪則很帥，Sammi留言笑說：「肥美的飄紅。」<br />\n<br />\n其實當年這部劇很受歡迎，Sammi飾演的孖生姊妹飄紅和飄雪，愛上錢小豪飾演的張北平，是大家的童年回憶。Sammi此post一出，不少粉絲留言大讚偶像很美，既清純又可愛，有粉絲更留言希望有續集！該劇當年是由著名監製添哥（李添勝）操刀，現時已晉升導演的游乃海，是當年編劇之一，難怪劇本如此吸引有趣！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2zT02mt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zT02mt&d=mSaaklrB3SRJE07mHO5empUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=116bc6b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2zT02mt</a>"},{"pid":"6c3cb7ea5ec3cb3dcacb4cf0dcacfb03bff56676","tid":848699,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"真係唔敢相信佢拍瘦身男女果陣肥到欣宜咁都可以減到"},{"pid":"acb03956a6aeec41e5a289b2530fa8eaa70b782a","tid":848699,"uid":65024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c3cb7ea5ec3cb3dcacb4cf0dcacfb03bff56676","tid":848699,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"真係唔敢相信佢拍瘦身男女果陣肥到欣宜咁都可以減到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52e9850e37083e42e939ff0477ac02c79450786","tid":848699,"uid":202557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c3cb7ea5ec3cb3dcacb4cf0dcacfb03bff56676","tid":848699,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"真係唔敢相信佢拍瘦身男女果陣肥到欣宜咁都可以減到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  假架特技化妝"},{"pid":"fe2a744f32c64895f51786f5a85e3d405b6a84eb","tid